summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting the redevelopment proposal of SEATTLE HABITAT FOR HUMANITY to purchase and develop Parcel 75 in the Yesler/Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (Wash. R-5) area; authorizing the Mayor to execute and deliver contracts and deeds; authorizing the Director of Housing and Human Services to administer the "Contract for Sale of Land"; designating the disposition of sales proceeds; and ratifying and confirming prior actions.
committee: Housing, Community Development and Urban Environment
